generic

Class Variable

  • java.lang.Object
    • generic.Variable

  • public class Variable
extends java.lang.Object
    Variable is the class that creates a variable. It has various characteristics: variable name, variable type, variable interval, where the user can choose the minimum value and the maximum value, and the variable weight, because there are variables that are more important then others.
    Author:
    Nuno Fialho EIC1 72910, Sandro Ferreira EIC1 72911, Duarte Pinto EIC1 73117
